source.name: Fire Incidents
source.description: Fire Incidents includes a summary of each (non-medical) incident to which the SFFD responded. Each incident record includes the call number, incident number, address, number and type of each unit responding, call type (as determined by dispatch), prime situation (field observation), actions taken, and property loss. Addresses are associated with a block number, not with a specific address.
